# Do Not Run Paid Vocabulary Scripts

The scripts in `scripts/vocabulary/` that call the Anthropic API cost real money on every run. You are FORBIDDEN from executing them yourself.

This applies to (any script that hits `https://api.anthropic.com`), including:
- `scripts/vocabulary/find-phrasal-verbs.mts`
- `scripts/vocabulary/find-idioms.mts`
- `scripts/vocabulary/find-proper-names.mts`
- `scripts/vocabulary/to-lemma-forms.mts`

Rules:
- NEVER run these scripts via `node`, `tsx`, or any other command, even to verify a change.
- You MAY edit these scripts, read them, and reason about them.
- After making changes, ask the USER to run the script themselves and report the output.

The offline script `scripts/vocabulary/find-phrasal-verb-candidates.mts` does NOT call the API and is safe to run.
